    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dreamwalker is a top-down story RPG game with deckbuilding combat.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey through dreams and nightmares in Dreamwalker, a 2D top-down RPG set in a mesmerizing pixel art world. You are a wandering traveler, drawn to a small village shrouded in mystery and cursed by an ancient evil.     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🃏 <strong>Deckbuilding Combat</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your starter deck</strong> and forge your own playstyle as you collect, upgrade, and craft a unique deck tailored to your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Visit merchants</strong> to buy, sell, upgrade, and trade up cards to refine your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200+ unique cards</strong> across 4 rarities (Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary), featuring upgradable and combinable effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat with animated enemies. Face different elemental foes with special Moves: Stuns, poison, burn, deck disruption, and more - forcing you to adapt as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/extras/23cc116afd0111941e0bdc286dac2ca7.poster.avif?t=1766170571\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/extras/23cc116afd0111941e0bdc286dac2ca7.webm?t=1766170571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/extras/23cc116afd0111941e0bdc286dac2ca7.mp4?t=1766170571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💤 <strong>Enter a World of Living Dreams</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each villager’s mind is its <strong>own world</strong>—a haunted castle, a shifting marketplace, or a forest of glowing memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each dream holds <strong>secrets, challenges, and unexpected allies</strong> waiting to be discovered.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete quests, solve intricate puzzles, and shape the story with your decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn powerful new cards and Dreamtokens to strengthen your deck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
